{
  "stem": "1858.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 428.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She says, oh, I bet you it's one of my cousins.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You cannot imagine, you cannot picture, the sight of when she came from factory-- and my other sister-- and there I stood, waiting for them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I cannot describe to you the shock.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They realized that something is wrong.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why am I, at my age-- well, I lied about my age and so did my father because by all rights, I should not have been in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I should not have been sent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was too young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father said that I was 16.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know, and I said 15.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But somehow-- they also looked for girls with small hands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that sort of saved me because when the hauptfuhrer asked, 'kannst du arbeiten?' I said, yeah-- can you work?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because at first, I was assigned to a very long, long machine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It had tiny little spindles, you know, like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the spool of thread was right in the middle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If that spool tore or got stuck, you had to stop the spindle one at a time, while the rest of the machine was running.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So if you had big hands, you couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So all the girls with small hands were assigned to that machine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What we were producing is, out of flax, we were making thread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, eventually, the finished product was a German uniform.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Again, we were working to help the Nazis fight the war against us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As I said, we worked 12- to 14-hour shifts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And every time, when my machine was giving me problems, I was kept busy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it was the time when the machine was running smoothly that it was the worst because it was then that I had time to daydream, contemplate, think of home.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
